n></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</p>\n</details>\n<h3 id=\"3-安装Redis、fileinfo\"><a href=\"#3-安装Redis、fileinfo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.安装Redis、fileinfo\"></a>3.安装Redis、fileinfo</h3><p>宝塔面板 &gt; 软件商店 &gt; 找到PHP7.4 点击设置 &gt; 安装扩展 &gt; redis,fileinfo 进行安装。</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-解除被禁止的函数\"><a href=\"#4-解除被禁止的函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.解除被禁止的函数\"></a>4.解除被禁止的函数</h3><p>宝塔面板 &gt; 软件商店 &gt; 找到PHP7.4 点击设置 &gt; 禁用函数 &gt; 将 putenv、proc_open、pcntl_alarm、pcntl_signal 从列表中删除。</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-添加站点\"><a href=\"#5-添加站点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.添加站点\"></a>5.添加站点</h3><p>宝塔面板 &gt; 网站 &gt; 添加站点。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在 域名 填入你指向服务器的域名</li>\n<li>在 数据库 选择MySQL</li>\n<li>在 PHP版本 选择PHP-74</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"6-开启SSL\"><a href=\"#6-开启SSL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.开启SSL\"></a>6.开启SSL</h3><p>宝塔面板 &gt; 网站 &gt; 找到你的站点 点击设置 &gt; SSL &gt; Let’s Encrypt</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在 验证方式 选文件验证</li>\n<li>在 域名 选择你的域名</li>\n<li>点击申请 成功后 开启 强制HTTPS</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"7-安装V2Board\"><a href=\"#7-安装V2Board\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7.安装V2Board\"></a>7.安装V2Board</h3><p>通过SSH登录到服务器后访问站点路径如：&#x2F;www&#x2F;wwwroot&#x2F;你的站点域名。<br>以下命令都需要在站点目录进行执行。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /www/wwwroot/你的站点域名\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 删除目录下文件</span>\n$ chattr -i .user.ini\n$ <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> -rf .htaccess <span class=\"token number\">404</span>.html index.html .user.ini\n$ <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> -rf .well-known/<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>终端执行演示</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">root@debian:~<span class=\"token comment\"># cd /www/wwwroot/你的站点域名</span>\nroot@debian:/www/wwwroot/你的站点域名<span class=\"token comment\"># chattr -i .user.ini</span>\nroot@debian:/www/wwwroot/你的站点域名<span class=\"token comment\"># rm -rf .htaccess 404.html index.html .user.ini</span>\nroot@debian:/www/wwwroot/你的站点域名<span class=\"token comment\"># rm -rf .well-known/</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</p>\n</details>\n<p>执行命令从 Github 克隆到当前目录。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/v2board/v2board.git ./<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>终端执行演示</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">root@debian:/www/wwwroot/你的站点域名<span class=\"token comment\"># git clone https://github.com/v2board/v2board.git ./</span>\nCloning into <span class=\"token string\">'.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\nremote: Enumerating objects: <span class=\"token number\">16891</span>, done.\nremote: Counting objects: <span class=\"token number\">100</span>% <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">696</span>/696<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, done.\nremote: Compressing objects: <span class=\"token number\">100</span>% <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">274</span>/274<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, done.\nremote: Total <span class=\"token number\">16891</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>delta <span class=\"token number\">442</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, reused <span class=\"token number\">635</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>delta <span class=\"token number\">403</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, pack-reused <span class=\"token 